away from us.

39:56.330 --> 39:58.790
Because
they are terrified.

39:58.790 --> 40:00.750
Because
they are outraged.

40:00.750 --> 40:02.460
Because they have
come to the realization

40:02.460 --> 40:06.000
that all those centuries
of misogyny and privilege

40:06.000 --> 40:08.380
and status quo
are finally over.

40:08.380 --> 40:11.380
This is why you never listen
to a man over me.

40:11.380 --> 40:14.040
Your success as President
is my only agenda.

40:14.040 --> 40:17.330
I, alone, have your back --
always.

40:17.330 --> 40:19.580
You want to keep the barbarians
at the gate?

40:19.580 --> 40:21.330
You want to
hold these walls?

40:21.330 --> 40:23.210
You want to keep
having it all,

40:23.210 --> 40:26.880
reverse the tides of injustice,
redraw the map,

40:26.880 --> 40:28.790
flood the darkness with light,

40:28.790 --> 40:31.120
earn our place and make it so
that woman holding this office

40:31.120 --> 40:33.500
