but the norm?

40:33.500 --> 40:36.290
Then you have to stop
thinking of me as an employee

40:36.290 --> 40:38.040
and start thinking of me
as what I am.

40:38.040 --> 40:39.330
And what is that?

40:39.330 --> 40:40.710
The boss.

40:40.710 --> 40:43.000
Put your faith in me
and me alone,

40:43.000 --> 40:46.380
and you will become
a monument.

40:46.380 --> 40:51.000
Ignore me,
allow them to come between us,

40:51.000 --> 40:52.880
and you will become
an asterisk.

40:52.880 --> 40:55.000
