41:57.750 --> 42:00.120
♪ Everything you have is yours
and not stolen ♪

42:00.120 --> 42:02.380
Olivia: So, you tell me,
which one do you want to be?

42:02.380 --> 42:05.040
♪ So don't just stand there,
